%^BOLD%^-=%^BLACK%^Darkness Domain%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

By channelling the powers of darkness, the caster can create a range of spells that protect him, cause damage to his foes, and finally allow him to spy upon those who are far away.

The darkness domain contains the following spells:

Shadow Stream, Fog Cloud, Blindness, Armor of Darkness, Shadow Conjuration, Darkbolt, Shadow Travel, Powerword Blind, Listening Shadow, Shades

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Lord Shadow, The Faceless One

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
